      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">
      Papers of the farmer and soldier, free soil advocate, son of abolitionist John Brown 
		(1800-1859).   13 combination diary/account books (1856-1895), and 3 letters of his 
		father to family members.</abstract>
